items.ittfWrapped:
scss 
    @import 'base'
    . container
        @extend .flex-column-center
        @ align-items center
        @ justify-content flex-start
        @ height 100%
        @ width 100%
        @ font-weight 400
        @ padding-top 1.5rem
    . panel
        @extend .flex-column-center
        @ justify-content center
        @ padding 1.25rem
        @ width 35%
        @include mobile
            { 
                @ width 75%
        @ min-width 250px
        @ min-height 270px
    . or
        @ margin-top 1rem
        @ margin-bottom .5rem
        @ font-size 1.3rem
    . signup
        @extend .flex-column-center
        @ justify-content center
        @ margin-top 2rem
        & Link
            @ color $linkBlue;
            @ font-size 1.2rem
            & 
                : hover
                @ color $materialBlue;
        & Label
            @ font-size 1.3rem
            @ font-size 1rem
            @ font-weight bold
            @ color $mediumGray
            @ font-weight 400
    . providers
        @ margin-top 1rem
